@toc Main
@node Features

@{i}Features@{ui}

    dl2 features:

        *       An AppIcon for easy drag-and-drop of files

        *       More then one file can be dropped onto the AppIcon.

        *       Ability to add new file types/descriptions through the use of the Amiga's DataType system.

        *       Fully compatible with OS3.0

        *       Displays the file size of file in question

        *       Allows the use of any Icon. NewIcons have been used successfully with dl2.



@{"<--" LINK "Main"} @{i}Back to Main Page@{ui}

@endnode
@node Installation

@{i}Installation@{ui}

    dl2 can now be dragged into your SYS:WBStartUp drawer and run everytime you start your computer!

    An Icon file called "Icon.info" (ie an icon :> ) must be in the same directory as dl2. This icon can be the one
    that is included with this distribution, or it can be one of yuor own choice. (I'm not an artist :> )

    The easy way to do this is to use IconEdit to create your icon and then save it!










@{"<--" LINK "Main"} @{i}Back to Main Page@{ui}
@endnode

@node Configuration

@{i}Configuration@{ui}

    Configuration is performed using the supplied "dlPrefs" programme.

    See the enclosed "dlPrefs.guide" file for more information

    ** NEW **

    With the removal of the file logging code in v2.22 and higher, the prefs files are no
    longer needed. This means that dl2 will no longer log to a file.

    If people find this to Be A Bad Thing (tm) then EMail me and I'll fix it :)






@{"<--" LINK "Main"} @{i}Back to Main Page@{ui}
@endnode

@node Running

@{i}Running the Programme@{ui}

    Whilst the programme is running, there will be an app-icon on the screen.

    Dragging an icon onto this app-icon will result in a window opening up that displays the file name and the filetype. This window can be closed by clicking on the "OK" button.

    dl2 can be exited by double clicking on the app-icon and selecting "QUIT".










@{"<--" LINK "Main"} @{i}Back to Main Page@{ui}
@endnode

@node De-installing

@{i}Removing dl2@{ui}

    Simply delete the dl2 programme and Icon..















@{"<--" LINK "Main"} @{i}Back to Main Page@{ui}

@endnode

