@node Future

@{i}Future Plans@{ui}

    I hope to have dl3.0 running as a commodity.

    (That is, so long as people let me know what they think of my programme :> )

    Also, I hope to have dl3.0 distributed with an Install/Remove script, and if Phase V release the PPC Amiga's then I'll have a PPC version ready for that too :)



