@node New

@{i}New Features@{ui}

    @{b}Version 2.22@{ub}

    *   Removed File logging code.

    *   Deleted the dlPrefs file from the distribution.

    @{b}Version 2.21@{ub}

    *   Changed the Icon image to be one of your own choice.

    @{b}Version 2.20@{ub}

    *   Added FILE-LOGGING support to the code.

    *   Completed the Preferences file.

    *   Fixed an annoying little "i++" in the appmessage loop :)


    @{b}Version 2.15@{ub}

    *   Fixed bug in my "Wait()" code.

    *   Altered format of the dl.prefs file

    *   Moved dl.prefs from ENV: to ENVARC:

    *   Changed the way the preferences file is read in.

    @{b}Version 2.10@{ub}

    *   Created a new icon for the appicon.

    *   Fixed the $VER tag so that it showed the correct version.

    *   Added LOGGING to a GUI Window.

    @{b}Version 2.00@{ub}

    *   Added an AppIcon

    @{b}Version >1.90@{ub}

    *   CLI version of programme. Replaced with GUI version :)

